data.description: Assumable mortgage alert, 2.99%! Hallmark Movie class and charm! Country Living but only 5 minutes to Riverwalk - you have to see this amazing property! Welcoming sitting porch with gorgeous wood pillars and accent shutters. French doors, natural light, modern color scheme throughout with white trim and dark-finished hardwood floors upstairs with radiant floor heating; beautiful kitchen cabinetry, hard surface countertops and all modern appliances; stylish updated bathrooms with modern vanities and vessel sinks; large bedrooms with closet space; fully finished carpeted basement; water heater replaced. ENTIRE property is completely fenced. Detached garage (50amp). Workshop (50amp).  2 separate 1 car carports. RV area w/ electric hookup and water connections (dedicated 30amp). Newer roof on main house and barn. Drip irrigation system. Well water allows for beautiful trees, plants and grass to flourish.
